Description: # dippy
        
        Dippy is DIP(Digital Image Processing) in Python3.
        
        This library depends on Numpy only.
        
        
        ## Installation
        
        ```
        $ pip install dip-python
        ```
        
        ## Features
        
        ### Algorithm
        
        - [ ] Convert
            - [x] Inverse NegPog
            - [x] Color
                - [x] rgb2gray
                - [x] rgb2bgr
                - [x] rgb2hsv
            - [x] binarize
                - [x] threshold
                - [x] otsu
            - [ ] Histgram Equalization
            - [x] Tonecurve
                - [x] Polygonal
                - [x] Gamma
                - [x] Posterization
                    - [x] Nearest Neighhbor
                    - [x] Equality
            - [ ] Dithering(support 2way)
                - [x] Nearest Neighbor
                - [x] Floyd-Steinberg
                - [x] Sierra Lite
                - [x] Atkinson
                - [ ] Poison Disk Sampling
            - [ ] Declease Color
                - [x] kMeans
        - [ ] Filtering
            - [ ] Spatial
                - [ ] Average
                - [ ] Weighted Average
                - [ ] Gaussian
                - [ ] Prewitt
                - [ ] Sobel
                - [ ] Laplacian
                - [ ] Sharping
                - [ ] k-Nearest Neighbor
                - [ ] Bilateral
                - [ ] Non-Local Mean
                - [ ] Median
            - [ ] Freaquency
                - [ ] Low Pass
                - [ ] High Pass
                - [ ] Band Pass
                - [ ] High Emphasis
                - [ ] Gaussian Low Pass
                - [ ] Gaussian High Pass
                - [ ] Gaussian Band Pass
                - [ ] Gaussian High Emphasis
        - [ ] Resize
            - [ ] Nearest Neighbor
            - [x] Bi-Linear
            - [ ] Bi-Cubic
            - [ ] Lanczos
        - [ ] Image Operation
            - [ ] Alpha Blending
            - [ ] Emboss
            - [ ] Mask
        
        ### Utils
        
        - [ ] I/O
            - [x] BMP
            - [x] PNG
            - [ ] JPEG
            - [ ] GIF
        - [ ] Drawing
            - [ ] Line
            - [ ] Rectangle
            - [ ] Circle
            - [ ] Fonts
        
        ### Extra
        
        - [x] Print
            - [x] Braile
            - [x] AA
            - [x] Animation
        - [ ] TUI
            - [x] Print
                - [x] Image
                - [x] Histgram
                - [x] Spectrum
            - [ ] Processing
        
